bbsAssistant 2.0.0
  • Reference

    Species List Lookup Table

    species_list.Rd

    Species List Associated with Most Recent BBS Dataset Release

    species_list

    Format

    An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 2385 rows and 11 columns.

    Details

    Seq

    row identifier used by BBS

    AOU

    species-level numeric code used by BBS

    English_Common_Name

    Common name in English

    French_Common_Name

    Common name in French

    Spanish_Common_Name

    Common name in Spanish

    ORDER

    taxonomic order

    Family

    taxonomic family

    Genus

    taxonomic genus

    Species

    taxonomic species epithet

    Scientific_Name

    comprised of the Genus and Species as provided in BBS dataset

    AOU4

    4-letter alpha code from IBP AOU data (Seq4) https://www.birdpop.org/pages/birdSpeciesCodes.php. Ths should be double-checked when using for analytical purposes.

    AOU6

    4-letter alpha code from IBP AOU data (Seq6)https://www.birdpop.org/pages/birdSpeciesCodes.php. Ths should be double-checked when using for analytical purposes.
